{"word":"H3510 - כּאב - kâ'ab - kaw-ab'","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: כּאב"},{"paragraph":"Transliteration: kâ'ab"},{"paragraph":"Phonetic: kaw-ab'"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - துக்கமாயிரு, துயரமாயிரு, சஞ்சலப்படு, நோவிரு, கெடு, காயப்படு, நோவுண்டாக்கு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to be in pain, to be sore, to have pain, to be sorrowful"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to be in pain (physical)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"2) to be in pain (mental)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Hiphil)"},{"paragraph":"1) to cause pain, to hurt, to mar"},{"paragraph":"2) pain, mar (participle)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Cognate: <a href=\"https://wordofgod.in/bibledictionary/ஸ்ட்ராங்க்ஸ்-எபிரேய-அகராதி/#/H3510 - כּאב - kâ'ab - kaw-ab'/3510\">H3510</a>, <a href=\"https://wordofgod.in/bibledictionary/ஸ்ட்ராங்க்ஸ்-எபிரேய-அகராதி/#/H3511 - כּאב - ke'êb - keh-abe'/3511\">H3511</a>, <a href=\"https://wordofgod.in/bibledictionary/ஸ்ட்ராங்க்ஸ்-எபிரேய-அகராதி/#/H4341 - מכאבה מכאוב מכאב - mak'ôb mak'ôb mak'ôbâh - mak-obe'/4341\">H4341</a>"}]}